description:
Course set out

  • Introduction into homeopathy, dosage and how to use the remedy.
  • before birth and what remedy to use in certain circumstances eg late labour
  • during labour and what remedy to use when.
  • after labour for speed of recovery and pain
  • you will receive manual and powerpoint slide
  • there will be a quiz so you can pratice what you have learnt

This course is easy to follow combination of video presentations, powerpoint slides, hand outs of powerpoint slide with remedy information and more.
title: Homeopathy in Childbirth
